remarks:
Aerodrome traffic circuits:
RWY 17: on the right,
RWY 35: on the left.

Arrival and departure to/from aerodrome is subject of ATC clearance from SLIAČ TOWER 122,905 MHz (MIL TWR LZSL TEL: +421/960/45 21 22).
Taxiing to the take-off point on RWY 17 or after landing on RWY 35 is carried out on the RWY itself.
Note:
FREQ 118,140 MHz is used only in the time when local traffic activity at Dobrá Niva aerodrome is declared.
